Changes in version 2.6 (12) from 2014-02-26
===========================================

 * Revise volume level preference
 * Append more optional sample rate values
 * Make some cosmetic changes

Changes in version 2.5 (11) from 2014-01-01
===========================================

 * Fix saving audio thread specific preferences
 * Fix early added headset fallback mode
 * Add VAD based automute function
 * Add signal offset correction
 * Add a button to reset preferences
 * Add the changelog dialog
 * Add new info activites
 * Make various user interface changes

Changes in version 2.4 (10) from 2013-10-26
===========================================

 * Add wired headset fallback if no Bluetooth device available
 * Make some small improvements

 (this release is only available on F-Droid)

Changes in version 2.3 (9) from 2012-09-26
==========================================

 * Enhanced Bluetooth support
 * Added LogCat output

Changes in version 2.2 (8) from 2012-09-17
==========================================

 * Fixed the Bluetooth permission issue
 * Some small fixes made

Changes in version 2.1 (7) from 2012-08-28
==========================================

 * Source code revised for the F-Droid
 * Small fixes made

Changes in version 2.0 (6) from 2012-08-22
==========================================

 * Revised GUI
 * Introduced background audio processing
 * Added Bluetooth support
 * Added sound amplifier feature

Changes in version 1.4 (5) from 2012-06-16
==========================================

 * Added detune effect
 * Performed refactoring (JAVA & C/C++)
 * Removed Secret Rabbit Code (it's sadly too large)

Changes in version 1.3 (4) from 2012-06-07
==========================================

 * Performed refactoring (JAVA)
 * Added preferences for volume level, denoising and sample rate
 * Fixed bug: loud tone while transposing (incomplete phase buffer initialisation)

